OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy with patchy light
OL,6,Frain in the west during the morning.
OL,7,FThe rain will spread east and become
OL,8,Fheavier near the west coast in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. North Highland staying
OL,10,Fmainly dry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy in the
OL,13,Fevening as rain spreads northeast,
OL,14,Fheavier for a time in the west. This
OL,15,Fclears overnight, becoming dry for a
OL,16,Ftime, before further rain in west
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
