OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain in
OL,6,Fthe west at first. This spreading east
OL,7,Fand becoming heavy for a time. Then
OL,8,Fclearing to bright spells and showers
OL,9,Fin evening. Occasionally windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,Ffrom Monday to Wednesday, these heavy
OL,14,Fand thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
